<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.1.6">
<l>tuvari yāṭaiyar maṭṭai yarcamaṇ toṇṭar kaḷmaṇṭi yuṇṭu piṉṉarum</l>
<l>tamarum tāṅkaḷu mēta ṭikkaveṉ neñcamaṉpāy</l>
<l>kavari mākkaṇañ cērum vēṅkaṭaṅ kōyil koṇṭakaṇ ṇārvi cumpiṭai</l>
<l>yamara nāyakaṟ kiṉṟa ṭimaittoḻil pūṇṭāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My companion heart, today you assumed the duty of service</l>
<l>To the lord of the immortals in spacious heaven who has a temple</l>
<l>At Vēṅkaṭam with herds of yak, while Jain devotees,</l>
<l rend="indent">who wear saffron robes and are bald,</l>
<l>Having eaten greedily, they, [their] followers, and relative get fat.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
